Welcome to WorkerPool's documentation!
======================================

This is the documentation for WorkerPool project. It is a simple tool used to download the top 50 websites from each country and store them on the disk. It is a part of the project for the course "Python Programming" at the Faculty of Computer Science, Alexandru Ioan Cuza University of Iasi.
